name: Scenes of Geoda 04
description:
“Scenes of Geoda 04”
4525px x 3200px PNG
Digitally Drawn Artwork

A drawing taken from the Book of Geoda depicting the alchemist, Xeng brokering peace with a tribe leader by offering his book of recordings in exchange for safe passage through the ancient ruins of Maru. Meanwhile an ancient void guardian, a reawakened giant of old watches on curiously.
